---
title: Lemon Pepper Chicken & Honey Yoghurt with Roast Root Veggie Salad & Caramelised Onion
description: We’ve been digging for gold and now we finally have it! These root veggies are priceless additions to a salad, hearty
and earthy, they add volumes of flavour to zesty pepper chicken bites. The crowning jewel is a sweet honey yoghurt!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
